{"tid":1879822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動『有不反』元朗區議員領頭！15/2 宏逸見！","createTime":"2020-02-14T11:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T10:56:17.000Z","uid":143131,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa2b2fc2676a734a548597cc6dfb9b9a97c4071","tid":1879822,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"Copy from 郭文浩議員Facebook<br />\n<br />\n【#不反對通知書已發出📢 #聽日宏逸廣場❗❗】<br />\n<br />\n今日警方向 #無諮詢 #無交代 #反對天業路社區健康中心 變 武漢肺炎指定診所 遊行發出 #不反對通知書 ！<br />\n.<br />\n明天2點30分 ，宏逸廣場見大家💪<br />\n.<br />\n遊行詳情﹕<br />\n🚩日期﹕2月15日(明天)<br />\n.<br />\n🚩時間﹕ 2點30分集合，3點出發<br />\n.<br />\n🚩集合地點﹕ 宏逸廣場 (靈愛小學旁邊) <br />\n.<br />\n🚩遊行路線👣﹕ 宏逸廣場 &rarr;  天秀路公園 &rarr;  天秀路 &rarr; 天晴邨一期&rarr; 天葵路北行線行人路 &rarr;  慧景軒對出行人路(終點) <br />\n.<br />\n出席議員﹕<br />\n#郭文浩 #巫啟航 #關俊笙 #林進 #區國權 #吳玉英 #李俊威 #張智陽 #陳樹暉 #李煒鋒 #何惠彬 #陳詩雅 #陳美蓮 #伍軒宏 #王百羽 #黎寶華 #侯文健 #伍健偉 #方浩軒 #張秀賢 #黎國泳 #陳敬倫<br />\n .<br />\n#聽日見 #全民抗疫 #欠諮詢 #無交代<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucuwDfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucuwDfF.jpg&h=b461fa6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd6a58e6e7d47f3af7f8abadc899829b7e7965cc","tid":1879822,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"443741e4b6b3e5aa1c59a17bb414ff2ca3969b3e","tid":1879822,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9a13f8467cc34356edab321d790e2a1ec9195e55","tid":1879822,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"今次無伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家出嚟啦！腳痕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54659e4073da99a814b2fd9d07c3e050ddb2410b","tid":1879822,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"區外人<br />\n<br />\n唔知來唔來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c